},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:44:39.000Z","msg":"做明線就正常好平姐 你搵得人 最基本2000起嫁啦 假設係其中一個制有時"},{"pid":"0cbd938e23a0d51c332dbeb6f414f5b306035412","tid":2462093,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a0642b5bd8c27e2eb9c5ab721e9ef3f883cf297","tid":2462093,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9f50475e88d4a91a809e199a85e7194945d387","tid":2462093,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cabeae7b7159d28c28e7ed2aca13f7ac012cc9f9","tid":2462093,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:41:33.000Z","msg":"接近50年樓齡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:42:21.000Z","msg":"租定酒店搵師父放線都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"幾錢左右<br />\n<br />\n怕比人劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:45:07.000Z","msg":"唔知價 分分鐘要打牆你個d牆身線<br />\n不過你叫師傅跟跟先可能插蘇位d 線師傅駁返就無事"},{"pid":"e7fa30a5df31f4293b37091a71aec20e40e5f118","tid":2462093,"uid":50069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f001a331c00be8c2bbeafa8be687dd5af75b2c","tid":2462093,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b3687086aa8137b94b9e6cc76a5ab5cb071671","tid":2462093,"uid":50069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7568d2aa93d2ac869633e2fa4af399b8d7e0e50b","tid":2462093,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:31:13.000Z","msg":"試過拔哂房插頭都開唔返，我房牆後係廁所，<br />\n之前牆身試過有滲水問題<br />\n<br />\n諗緊關唔關事<br />\n<br />\n但幾個鐘前有人沖涼都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n反而而家先黎跳<br />\n<br />\n上個月都試過，兩日抽完濕又冇事，但成半個月都冇事今日無啦啦又黎料"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:37:49.000Z","msg":"冇電器插住都有事就係電制/電路有問題<br />\nFuse獨立熄左你房<br />\n其他照用先<br />\n<br />\n搵人上黎拆電制睇<br />\n可能濕左電線<br />\n<br />\n但你廁所防水有問題<br />\n都要開始諗重做<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩估"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:38:55.000Z","msg":"都可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n師兄估整電制電線呢d大約幾錢左右？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:45:30.000Z","msg":"搵人拆左制睇先啦<br />\n可能係濕左個制/制盒<br />\n咁樣就簡單好多<br />\n<br />\n因為中間電線<br />\n理論上有pvc膠管<br />\n冇咁易有水入<br />\n但唔可以排除<br />\n<br />\n你防水有問題<br />\n拉過哂d線都未必有用<br />\n因為過一排又係會濕過<br />\n<br />\n散做電制拉線就好似1200蚊一隻<br />\n換制面就300-500<br />\n但唔知有冇人會咁樣同你做<br />\n<br />\n重做廁所就10皮起"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e6a55d6451f2eb7a0c087efc8ba4757ff497a773","tid":2462093,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:50:19.000Z","msg":"我又唔可以肯定，因為個fuse除咗我房仲有走廊，廚房同廳既一盞燈<br />\n<br />\n但我已經關哂全部電<br />\n<br />\n都開唔返個fuse"}}